@startuml IsExist

actor User
participant "BaseServiceImpl" as BSI
participant "ValidationUtils" as VU
participant "Repository" as REP

== Check Existence ==
User -> BSI: isExist(id)
activate BSI

BSI -> VU: Validate existence of ID
activate VU
VU --> BSI: Validation complete
deactivate VU

BSI --> User: Confirm existence
deactivate BSI

@enduml
